[Play As the Referee Codes\Press Select & L1 to Play as the Referee in a Two Character Match]
author=tokidoim
description=Must be pressed & held during the loading screen after the entrances. Press Square to count a pinfall or out of ring count. Make sure that Interference is set to "OFF". If is it set to "Manual" & one of the characters is part of a stable or tag team, then you'll play as one of the interfering characters.
