[Match Rules Codes\Tag Team / Tornado Tag Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=If set to Tag Team, Players must tag their partner for them to be legal in the ring, which means the illegal partner can't be pinned, submitted, or KOed. If set to Tornado Tag, all members of the tag team are legal in the ring & can be pinned, submitted, or KOed.
Values - 
00 - Tornado Tag
01 - Tag Team
